      content: "# ODF BASE VAULT\n\nBase de conocimiento para trading de opciones y mercados financieros.\n\n---\n\n## Estructura\n\n```\nODF-Base/\n├── .obsidian/              # Configuracion de Obsidian\n├── 00-MOC/                 # Maps of Content (indice)\n├── Bridges/                # Conexiones entre topics\n├── Catalysts/              # Eventos catalizadores (NFP, FOMC, CPI)\n├── Concepts/               # Conceptos fundamentales\n├── COT/                    # Commitment of Traders\n├── Greeks/                 # Greeks de opciones (Delta, Gamma, etc.)\n├── Lectures/               # 27 lecciones organizadas en 5 fases\n│   ├── Phase-1-Foundations/\n│   ├── Phase-2-Macro/\n│   ├── Phase-3-Options-Flow/\n│   ├── Phase-4-Order-Flow/\n│   └── Phase-5-Top-Bottom-Ticking/\n├── Macro-Drivers/          # Drivers macroeconomicos\n├── Microstructure/          # Microestructura del mercado\n├── Options-Flow/           # Flujo de opciones\n├── Orderflow/              # Analisis de orderflow\n├── Participants/           # Participantes del mercado\n├── Practice/               # Ejercicios practicos\n├── Profile-Levels/         # Niveles de profile (POC, VPOC, etc.)\n├── Quant/                  # Fundamentos cuantitativos\n├── Regimes/                # Regimenes de mercado\n├── Risk-Management/        # Gestion de riesgo\n└── Volatility/             # Volatilidad e IV\n```\n\n---\n\n## 5 Fases de Aprendizaje\n\n### Phase 1: Foundations (L1-L3)\n- Mercado de futuros\n- Pricing de futuros\n- Participantes del mercado\n\n### Phase 2: Macro (L4-L9)\n- Narrative framework\n- Variables macro\n- Bancos centrales\n- Relaciones intermarket\n- Calendario economico\n- Narrative shifts\n\n### Phase 3: Options Flow (L10-L15)\n- Options primer\n- Options chain\n- GEX y DEX\n- IV y Volatilidad\n- Actividad inusual\n- OPEX mechanics\n\n### Phase 4: Order Flow (L16-L21)\n- Microestructura\n- Footprint charts\n- Market Profile y AMT\n- COT Report\n- Liquidity sweeps\n- DOM y Tape Reading\n\n### Phase 5: Top Bottom Ticking (L22-L27)\n- Framework de tick\n- Senales de exhaustion\n- Integracion completa\n- Case studies\n- Risk management para reversals\n- Daily ritual\n\n---\n\n## Conceptos Clave\n\n### Regimenes\n- Long Gamma Regime\n- Short Gamma Regime\n- OpEx Pinning Regime\n- QE Regime\n\n### Conceptos\n- GEX / DEX\n- VPOC / POC\n- Adverse Selection\n- Bid Ask Spread\n- Orderflow\n- Liquidity\n\n### Greeks\n- Delta\n- Gamma\n- Theta\n- Vega\n\n---\n\n## Links\n\n### Relacionado\n- [[00-MOC\\MOC - Lectures]]\n- [[00-MOC\\MOC - Macro]]\n- [[00-MOC\\MOC - Options Flow]]\n- [[00-MOC\\MOC - Orderflow]]\n- [[00-MOC\\MOC - Risk Management]]\n\n### Bridges\n- [[Bridges\\Bridge - Macro Volatility Catalysts]]\n- [[Bridges\\Bridge - Participants and Market Structure]]\n- [[Bridges\\Bridge - Regimes to Strategies]]\n- [[Bridges\\Bridge - Risk Execution Psychology]]\n\n---\n\n## Estadisticas\n\n- **Lecciones**: 27 (L1-L27)\n- **Fases**: 5\n- **Conceptos**: 50+\n- **Docs totales**: 150+\n\n---\n\n## Uso\n\n1. Abrir en Obsidian\n2. Comenzar por Phase 1 o segun necesidad\n3. Usar MOCs como indice\n4. Seguir Bridges para conexiones\n\n---\n\n*Base: The foundation of knowledge*",
      wikilinks: ["00-MOC\\MOC - Lectures","00-MOC\\MOC - Macro","00-MOC\\MOC - Options Flow","00-MOC\\MOC - Orderflow","00-MOC\\MOC - Risk Management","Bridges\\Bridge - Macro Volatility Catalysts","Bridges\\Bridge - Participants and Market Structure","Bridges\\Bridge - Regimes to Strategies","Bridges\\Bridge - Risk Execution Psychology"],
