      content: "# FOMC Decision\n\n**Tags:** `#catalysts` `#fed` `#macro`\n**Links:** [[Lectures/Phase-2-Macro/L6 - Central Banks]] · [[Lectures/Phase-2-Macro/L8 - Economic Calendar]] · [[Macro-Drivers/Interest Rates]]\n\n**Protocol:** 2:00pm ET statement → 2:30pm press conference → Watch 2-year yield in real time.\nWait 5–15 minutes before acting on initial move (algos parsing). Real direction emerges in Q&A.\nSee full protocol: [[Lectures/Phase-2-Macro/L8 - Economic Calendar]]\n",
