      content: "# Long Gamma Regime\n\n**Tags:** `#regimes`\n**Links:** [[Concepts/GEX]] · [[Bridges/Bridge - Regimes to Strategies]] · [[HOME]]\n\n**Characteristics:** GEX positive, dealers dampen moves, mean-reverting market.\n**Strategy:** Fade extremes to VWAP/POC, range trade between call/put walls, tight stops.\n**Duration:** Typically pre-OPEX week and early in a new monthly cycle.\n**See:** [[Volatility/Volatility Regime]] · [[Concepts/GEX]]\n",
